rder to tackle the semantic gap. Furthermore, questions pertaining to the\norganization of these textual components into coherent structures that are\nusable in image indexing and retrieval frameworks shall arise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2020 05:27:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-06"}
